                td These settings define the support of serial numbers management of the selected Asset in the portal. Setting 
                    span.code tableColumns 
                    |defines the grid columns to be displayed in the given panel. The setting 
                    span.code fieldIDs 
                    |is used for locating the matching item instances in the BOM and viewer.
